OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fdry night with largely clear skies,
OL,7,Fwhich will give late sunshine in the
OL,8,Fevening. Overnight, a few mist and fog
OL,9,Fpatches may form inland.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FAny isolated mist and fog
OL,12,Fpatches will be quick clear leaving a
OL,13,Fdry day with light winds and
OL,14,Fpredominantly clear skies giving
OL,15,Fplenty of sunshine. Feeling warm in
OL,16,Fthe sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
